import axios from "axios"; export default function Login() { const base_url = process.env.REACT_APP_BASE_URL + ":8000/login" console.log(base_url) function auth(e) { e.preventDefault(); let data = new FormData(e.target); let data_to_send = { login: data.get('login'), password: data.get('password') } console.log(base_url) const result = axios.post(base_url, data_to_send) .then((result) => { console.log(result); }) .catch((error) => { console.log(error); }) } return ( <>
) }
